Consider the following recursive method. What is the output of `mystery(5)`?

```java
public int mystery(int n) {
    if (n == 1) {
        return 1;
    } else {
        return n + mystery(n - 1);
    }
}
```

What is the time complexity of the following recursive method for calculating a power?

```java
public double power(double x, int n) {
    if (n == 0) return 1;
    return x * power(x, n - 1);
}
```
